title: [Drake Harbor, Pier Five]
description: At the pier's end, a broad platform stretches over shimmering aquamarine waters.  Embedded into the wooden planks, a timeworn mariner's compass appears battered from both the weather and regular use.  Leaning against the sturdy railing, fishing rods await their next adventure.  Beyond the platform, the horizon blends sky and sea, offering a breathtaking view of the open waters.
